{"id":"6c916b73e3b7ad79fa92d44703e504e04161da7f","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1229233","title":"AI 果然让某些人变得更自信了","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"V2EX (创意工作者社区)","byline":"diudiuu","excerpt":"职场话题 - @diudiuu - 1. 已经陷入 AI 魔怔了，有问题你问 AI2. 听不得 AI 有关 AI 的坏话，如果你说 AI 有幻读，会胡说八道，它跟你急眼3. 舍不得花钱，天天在中转站薅羊毛4. 一个连需求都说","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div>\n    <div><P><a href=\"/tag/AI\"><li></li> AI</a><a href=\"/tag/自信\"><li></li> 自信</a><a href=\"/tag/讽刺\"><li></li> 讽刺</a></P><p><span>90 replies &#160;<strong>•</strong> &#160;2026-07-24 11:01:37 +08:00</span>\n    </p></div>\n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895425\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7b1432fd9577a14116e3971df74c876b?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"giter\" data-uid=\"476845\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>1</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/giter\">giter</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 11:23:30 +08:00\">23h 42m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 18</span>\n                    \n                    <p>《可是 AI 是这么回复我的》、《 AI 说的》、《稍等，我问下 AI 》</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895444\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/bda7ca9aa4308a060964140c2e42d0a4?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"connor123\" data-uid=\"577349\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>3</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/connor123\">connor123</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 11:25:50 +08:00\">23h 39m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>确实，办公室里有个项目经理，天天骂手底下的开发，说需求这么简单，ai 一下就干完了，你为什么要两天时间，你在干什么。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895485\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/c284ca7b0d652ec29f09be68ff7143d5?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"FantaMole\" data-uid=\"344641\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>5</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/FantaMole\">FantaMole</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 11:30:42 +08:00\">23h 35m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 3</span>\n                    \n                    <div><p>也可看出至少现阶段来说，AI 并不能作为所有人的外置大脑，为他们提升智力水平</p><p>然后对于没有信息搜集和分析能力的人来说，搜索时代和 AI 时代，对他们来说没有区别，无非一个是被百度骗，一个是被豆包骗</p></div>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895503\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f6f1/a31e/567497_normal.png?m=1743038632\" alt=\"wweerrgtc\" data-uid=\"567497\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>6</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/wweerrgtc\">wweerrgtc</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 11:33:29 +08:00\">23h 32m ago via iPhone</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 2</span>\n                    \n                    <p>ai 让我变强，我变强了当然更自信了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895543\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1de4265471582607d796903997063772?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"wu00\" data-uid=\"568801\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>7</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/wu00\">wu00</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 11:38:18 +08:00\">23h 27m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>一部分人是无脑跟风/怕被认为落伍/显摆  <br>另一部分人清醒，但是解释成本太高，所以~大家一起亩产万斤、吹泡泡才是最轻松的</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895567\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/75cf75395d4a05d96e1f605c28453f27?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"lnmput\" data-uid=\"175896\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>8</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/lnmput\">lnmput</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 11:41:03 +08:00\">23h 24m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>是 AI 变强了，不是你变强了，还有那是 AI 的能力，不是你的能力</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895585\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4ba9/a40c/62774_normal.png?m=1715075169\" alt=\"Aspx\" data-uid=\"62774\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>9</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Aspx\">Aspx</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 11:43:15 +08:00\">23h 22m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>农贝三是什么？</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895611\">\n        \n        <table>\n    