           </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895775\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/2b48/30a2/18392_normal.png?m=1755746557\" alt=\"revival83\" data-uid=\"18392\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>18</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/revival83\">revival83</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 12:25:45 +08:00\">22h 40m ago via iPhone</span> \n                    \n                    <p>用 Ai 没脑子的人最可怕</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895793\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a342/616e/400182_normal.png?m=1695690230\" alt=\"weiwenhao\" data-uid=\"400182\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>19</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/weiwenhao\">weiwenhao</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 12:34:46 +08:00\">22h 31m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 1</span>\n                    \n                    <p>我必须吐槽 AI 写的文档，那都不是人能读的。shit</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895842\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/607d/1db2/254229_normal.png?m=1716369049\" alt=\"jadewant\" data-uid=\"254229\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>23</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/jadewant\">jadewant</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 13:03:05 +08:00\">22h 2m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <div><p>很多时候，AI 确实成了一些人与别人“讨论”问题然后出现常识匮乏时的坚实后盾。</p><p>他们会把 AI 当权威，甚至生活中很多人都是这么干的，这大概是 AI 对人类目前最大的影响了。</p></div>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895857\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/85cf/7db0/514601_normal.png?m=1768439521\" alt=\"rockddd\" data-uid=\"514601\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>24</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/rockddd\">rockddd</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 13:07:17 +08:00\">21h 58m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>不得不说现在 Claude 和 gpt 用下来，我感觉比以前百度靠谱多了。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17895990\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ee6c9816fbec254923471fc2c30a6073?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"qwzhang01\" data-uid=\"339101\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>26</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/qwzhang01\">qwzhang01</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 13:40:54 +08:00\">21h 24m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>@<a href=\"/member/weiwenhao\">weiwenhao</a> 就是，以前看人写的需求，因为人懒，把最关键的写出来了<br>AI 现在不懒，关键信息 5 各自，需求文档 500 字，费劲</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17896150\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/93fc/90d6/666405_normal.png?m=1767083318\" alt=\"bello123\" data-uid=\"666405\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>29</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/bello123\">bello123</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 14:09:20 +08:00\">20h 56m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>我司大批量接入 cc 办公，上周末公司的订阅拼车号全部封了，这周群里都在唉声叹气，没了 cc 干不了活</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17896282\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/53c0/4118/1055_normal.png?m=1784773572\" alt=\"diudiuu\" data-uid=\"1055\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>33</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/diudiuu\">diudiuu</a></strong> &#160; <div><p>OP</p></div>&#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 14:29:48 +08:00\">20h 35m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>@<a href=\"/member/coderluan\">coderluan</a> 现实中没有这个功能，要么自己闭嘴，跑这个地方来下嘴炮。要么自己跑。不管哪个都阻挡不住我来发嘴炮</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17896303\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7631/061a/129725_normal.png?m=1759588504\" alt=\"AV1\" data-uid=\"129725\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>34</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/AV1\">AV1</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 14:32:44 +08:00\">20h 33m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 3</span>\n                    \n                    <p>自从 AI 兴起后 V2 版面的日常就是：<br>中转站薅羊毛了……<br>我用一天时间就 vibe 一个项目，不写一行代码……<br>某 AI 又降智/封杀/重置了……<br>……</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17896335\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/53c0/4118/1055_normal.png?m=1784773572\" alt=\"diudiuu\" data-uid=\"1055\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>35</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/diudiuu\">diudiuu</a></strong> &#160; <div><p>OP</p></div>&#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 14:38:16 +08:00\">20h 27m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 1</span>\n                    \n                    <p>@<a href=\"/member/AV1\">AV1</a> 手办<br>pdd<br>PDD<br>中转站<br>中转<br>linux do<br>Linux do<br>Linux .do<br>重置<br>codex  这是我的屏蔽词</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17896359\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2124c8aba1b20643d71a5101a519a80d?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"zerovoid\" data-uid=\"263784\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>36</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/zerovoid\">zerovoid</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 14:42:27 +08:00\">20h 23m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>没啥区别，<br>以前就是《别人说的》《百度一下》，无非是现在换成《 AI 说的》</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\