     <div id=\"r_17897032\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7488/2140/500944_normal.png?m=1778216597\" alt=\"justdoitzZ\" data-uid=\"500944\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>46</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/justdoitzZ\">justdoitzZ</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 16:36:00 +08:00\">18h 29m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 1</span>\n                    \n                    <p>大家不都是草台班子嘛<br>区别是，我能够消化 AI 输出的内容<br>有的人，他妈的，喂到嘴里他都不吃，你的嚼碎了，喂到他胃里</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17897186\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/791ddde20df0d07cdfc303598adc51b5?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"nanxiaonan\" data-uid=\"420771\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>48</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/nanxiaonan\">nanxiaonan</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 17:02:08 +08:00\">18h 3m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>我们领导直接把他和 deep seek 的对话发出来 让我们参考写方案，其实一起参考意义都没有 和实际一点也不相符，纯属自嗨式想象。没有可执行性。更别说落地了。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17897232\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/53c0/4118/1055_normal.png?m=1784773572\" alt=\"diudiuu\" data-uid=\"1055\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>49</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/diudiuu\">diudiuu</a></strong> &#160; <div>