\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f5ab/0962/373417_normal.png?m=1550830481\" alt=\"xvb2421\" data-uid=\"373417\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>55</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/xvb2421\">xvb2421</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 18:26:51 +08:00\">16h 38m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>差不多，完全不过一遍，ai 直出</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17897593\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ee0/817f/276109_normal.png?m=1720859459\" alt=\"IamUNICODE\" data-uid=\"276109\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>56</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/IamUNICODE\">IamUNICODE</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 18:33:29 +08:00\">16h 32m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>最恐怖的是用 ai 甩屎好吧，用 ai 生成一堆漂亮需求给老板，然后这边根本没这个数据支持，老板一问就是为什么我们没有，因为我们不是做电商的肯定没有这个数据啊，然后产品毛事没有，反正我需求给你了，你自己筛选，能做的就做，不能就过，我靠</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17897782\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4a47/d5e9/634337_normal.png?m=1784644124\" alt=\"YGHMXFAL\" data-uid=\"634337\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>58</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/YGHMXFAL\">YGHMXFAL</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-23 19:53:11 +08:00\">15h 12m ago via Android</span> \n                    \n                    <p>我刚新开一帖提了一个技术问题,结果第二天谷歌搜索 AI 就把我的问题当成解决方案来引用了